监管部门追究其法律责任，由此产生的损失由用户自行承担。 本产品最终解释权归平台所有，若用户对产品有疑问，可通过官方客服渠道咨询。&lt;/p&gt;\n',6,0,1,'',1634644924,1773640150,NULL,30,30000.00000000,500000.00000000,0.00571500,'3%-22%',0),(11,11,'FIL',NULL,'/upload/20211019/b4a5933c1c3373766d445845f28ced05.png','en-us','&lt;p&gt;FIL&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634647618,1773633857,1773633857,7,1000.00000000,100000000.00000000,0.00263000,'3%~8%',1),(12,11,'FIL',NULL,'/upload/20211019/6a380ddcd9fa1f75106d3e7663281270.png','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;FIL&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634647820,1773633872,1773633872,15,10000.00000000,1000000000.00000000,0.00419000,'3%-12%',1),(13,11,'FIL',NULL,'/upload/20260310/61fc26ef436f3789d13bf848ba277659.jpg','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;FIL&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634648053,1773633865,1773633865,30,30000.00000000,50000000.00000000,0.00576000,'3%-22%',0),(14,1,'btc',NULL,'/upload/20260310/509913a482dfd7b6ea40dffa03830c51.jpg','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;btc&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634648282,1773634743,1773634743,7,1.00000000,1000.00000000,0.00571400,'3%~8%',0),(15,1,'BTC',NULL,'/upload/20211019/74dec9f8ff685c293135a3e7765bc9d8.png','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;BTC&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634648632,1773634737,1773634737,30,10.00000000,10000.00000000,0.01153000,'3%-22%',0),(16,2,'ETH',NULL,'/upload/20211019/ee4f99ddbd351c1183c36d2f3262494c.png','en-us','&lt;p&gt;ETH&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'',1634648848,1773633804,1773633804,60,50.00000000,500000.00000000,0.01149000,'3%~8%',0),(17,6,'USDT',NULL,'/upload/20260310/1e30c45e5b30486dc53d19b5182c0fed.jpg','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;USDT&amp;nbsp;描述&lt;/p&gt;\n',0,0,1,'USDT 描述备注',1773128456,1773633742,1773633742,1,1.00000000,10.00000000,0.05000000,'3%~9%',100),(18,2,'ETH',NULL,'/upload/20260316/9e73072821874f902af5f8334b458bb4.png','zh-cn','&lt;p&gt;本产品为Bitbumb平台专属ETH算力定存理财产品（Bitbumb computing power plan），以ETH（以太坊）为投资标的，属于非保本浮动收益型产品，依托Bitbumb平台算力相关资金运作逻辑，为Bitbumb用户提供专属资产增值福利与空投权益。&lt;br /&gt;\n产品名称：Bitbumb ETH算力定存理财计划（Bitbumb computing power plan）&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;投资标的：ETH（以太坊），需确保投资币种为合规发行的ETH，无虚假、仿冒风险&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;